<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.8">
<l>mañcucēr vāṉeri nīrnilaṅ kālivai mayaṅki niṉṟa</l>
<l>vañcucē rākkaiyai yaraṇamaṉ ṟeṉṟuyyak karuti ṉāyēl</l>
<l>cantucēr meṉmulaip poṉmalarp pāvaiyum tāmum nāḷum</l>
<l>vantucēr vallavāḻ collumā vallaiyāy maruvu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you intend to be saved, saying that this body where the five [senses] unite</l>
<l rend="indent">is no protection,</l>
<l>[But] remains a muddle of these: the sky with clouds, fire, water,</l>
<l rend="indent">earth, and wind,</l>
<l>Oh, heart, firmly embrace the way that tells of Vallavāḻ</l>
<l rend="indent">where the lady of the golden flower,</l>
<l>Her soft breasts with sandalwood, and he always come together.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
